name: Interplay Learning Player
summary: Interplay Learning is an online, on-demand learning experience platform delivering a growing catalog of courses for the skilled trades industry. Get the training you need to reach that next level in HVAC, Solar, Plumbing, Electrical, and Facility Maintenance. Plus, our catalog keeps growing. You’ll find hundreds of hours of training including video and scenario-based exercises across different equipment types. Hone your skills and be ready for whatever the real world throws at you.
